Scenario: The Pizza Shop
SNS: The customer places an order. SNS "broadcasts" that an order happened.

SQS Queue 1 (Kitchen): Gets a message to start cooking.

SQS Queue 2 (Accounting): Gets a message to generate an invoice.

Decoupling: Tell them: "If the Kitchen app crashes, the Accounting app still gets the message. That's why we use Queues!"

